comment_data.body:
`type.__dictoffset__` is not writable, so it seems a fatal error if `tp_dictoffset < 0` and no exception was raised. That should never happen.
```suggestion
    if (unlikely(tp_dictoffset == -1)) {
        assert(PyErr_Occurred());
        return NULL;
    }
```

